sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant S as Server
    alt is authorized
        C->>S: GET /data
        S-->>C: 200 OK
    else unauthorized
        S-->>C: 401 Unauthorized
    end
    opt retry on flake
        loop up to 3 times
            C->>S: retry
        end
    end
    par notify
        S->>C: event A
    and
        S->>C: event B
    end
